<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 02 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我覺得與特別朋友之間的
奢華問候語呀，<delay20 />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />是無可取代的友誼象徵喔！<pageBreak /><anim id="Hesitate" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我想要一個<delay8 />只屬於我們兩人的<delay20 />
秘密問候語呢。<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我試著自己想過了，<delay20 />
<anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過還沒想出好到能讓我拍板定案的<tag a="110" b="0" /><10_4 />
<anim id="Pardon" target="actor" targetSpec="" />希望你能給我一些意見，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="001_a" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="EmotEnd" target="player" targetSpec="" />這樣如何？</message>
	<message label="001_b" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">我想不到</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 02 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我想到<delay8 />一個好主意了！<pageBreak />我們兩人專屬的<delay8 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />「<tag a="110" b="14" />你　今　天　好　嗎　？<endTag a="110" b="14" />」這句
秘密問候語呀<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我覺得如果把它<delay8 />
換成全新的一句，<delay20 />
我們一定會有很新鮮的感覺！<pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />當然，我也覺得現在的問候語<delay8 />
沒什麼不好。<delay40 />
<anim id="Restless" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以我也沒有要勉強你的意思<tag a="110" b="0" />
<anim id="Pardon" target="actor" targetSpec="" />能讓我聽聽
<tag a="110" b="4" />的意見嗎？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002_a" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="EmotEnd" target="player" targetSpec="" />這樣如何？</message>
	<message label="002_b" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">維持現狀就好</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 02 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哎呀，<delay20 /><tag a="110" b="4" />。<pageBreak /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />呵呵，<delay20 />我正好在<delay20 />想一些事情呢。<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我剛才在想，如果要和朋友
<anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />用原創的問候語互相打招呼的話，<delay20 />
什麼樣的問候語才夠時髦呢？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003_a" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="EmotEnd" target="player" targetSpec="" />這樣如何？</message>
	<message label="003_b" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="EmotEnd" target="player" targetSpec="" />哦～</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 02 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Aha" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哎呀，<tag a="110" b="4" />！<delay20 />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你來得正好呢！<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />其實，<delay20 />我剛剛正在思考我們用的<delay8 />
「<tag a="110" b="14" />你　今　天　好　嗎　？<endTag a="110" b="14" />」
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這句問候語喔。<pageBreak /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />當然這句沒什麼不好，<delay20 />
不過我在想，要是能稍微再帶一點成熟的感覺，
是不是會更好<tag a="110" b="0" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay8 />
<anim id="Pardon" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你有什麼看法嗎？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004_a" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="EmotEnd" target="player" targetSpec="" />這樣如何？</message>
	<message label="004_b" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">維持現狀就好</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嗯～<delay20 />說的也是呢。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我也想了很久，<delay20 />
<anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但卻一直想不到
感覺夠好的問候語呢<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="006" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哎呀，這樣呀？<delay40 />
現在的問候語<delay8 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />的確也讓人難以割捨呢！<pageBreak /><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />呵呵，<delay8 />既然這麼決定了，
我們就好好珍惜，繼續用這句吧！<pageBreak /><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />能聽到<tag a="110" b="4" />你
真正的想法，<delay8 />真是太好了！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="007" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Restless" target="actor" targetSpec="" />難得有這樣的機會，<delay20 />我希望能想出一句
世界上獨一無二的問候語，<delay20 />
<anim id="Oops" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過一直都想不到呢……<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="008" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哎呀，這樣呀？<delay40 />不過，我的確也想不到<delay20 />能比
<tag a="110" b="14" />「你　今　天　好　嗎　？」<endTag a="110" b="14" /><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />更好的<delay20 />問候語了。<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />或許對我們而言，<delay20 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />現在這句還是最好的問候語呢！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="100" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />請告訴我吧，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="101" attrib="00 00 02 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />呵呵，我要來試用囉<tag a="110" b="0" /><10_4 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="14" />你　今　天　好　嗎　？<endTag a="110" b="14" /><delay40 />
<anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" />如何呀？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="101_a" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">還不錯啊</message>
	<message label="101_b" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">不對啦</message>
	<message label="102" attrib="00 00 02 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />「<tag a="110" b="14" />你　今　天　好　嗎　？<endTag a="110" b="14" />」<tag a="110" b="0" />？<delay40 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哎呀？<delay40 />果然還是
維持現狀比較好嗎？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="102_a" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">嗯</message>
	<message label="102_b" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">不對啦</message>
	<message label="103" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哎呀，對不起。<delay40 />
可以請你再告訴我一次嗎？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="104" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哎呀，<delay20 />你在煩惱要改成什麼樣的招呼語嗎？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不用急，慢慢想！<delay frames="40" />
好，<delay20 /><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />再來試一次吧？<tag a="110" b="6" />？</message>
	<message label="200" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="14" />你　今　天　好　嗎　？<endTag a="110" b="14" /><10_4 />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這句怎麼這麼好聽呀！</message>
	<message label="201" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="14" />你　今　天　好　嗎　？<endTag a="110" b="14" /><10_4 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />呵呵，<delay20 />這句問候語很不錯呢！</message>
	<message label="202" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我和<tag a="110" b="4" />之間的問候語，<delay20 />
就決定是這句了！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="203" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這真是兩人之間最棒的問候語！<delay40 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />感覺我和你<delay8 />真的非常親近呢！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="204" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />只屬於我們兩人的問候語，<delay20 />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真是讓人興奮呢！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="300" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那麼，<delay20 />就讓我們一如往常，<delay20 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />繼續使用<delay8 />「<tag a="110" b="14" />你　今　天　好　嗎　？<endTag a="110" b="14" />」
這句招呼語吧！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="301" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />呵呵，<delay20 />原來<tag a="110" b="4" /><delay8 />
很喜歡我們現在用的這句問候語呀。<pageBreak /><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那我們今後也好好珍惜，<delay8 />
繼續使用這句吧！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="302" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />「<tag a="110" b="14" />你　今　天　好　嗎　？<endTag a="110" b="14" />」<delay20 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這句問候語也充滿了<delay20 />
我和<tag a="110" b="4" />之間的寶貴回憶呢。<delay40 />
<anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />抱歉，問了你奇怪的問題。<delay40 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我們就好好珍惜，繼續使用這句吧，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
